        "content": "## WA-Inbound-Orchestrator\n\n### Funci\u00f3n\nPunto de entrada de todos los mensajes WhatsApp. Detecta pacientes nuevos, \ngestiona sesiones y enruta al agente IA.\n\n### Endpoints Django usados\n- GET /api/patients/?phone={phone} \u2014 Buscar paciente\n- GET /api/agent/sessions/?phone={phone} \u2014 Cargar sesi\u00f3n\n- POST /api/agent/sessions/ \u2014 Crear sesi\u00f3n  \n- PATCH /api/agent/sessions/{id}/ \u2014 Actualizar sesi\u00f3n\n- GET /api/appointments/?patient_phone={phone}&... \u2014 Verificar reminder pendiente\n\n### Sub-workflows invocados\n- WA-Patient-Onboarding (01xZkbBQIBBYCdK9) \u2014 paciente nuevo\n- WA-Appointments-Manager (rtLakHrc6xR9B8oH) \u2014 gesti\u00f3n citas (tool)\n- WA-Clinic-Info-RAG (43XUwyqUHZn1KBT2) \u2014 info cl\u00ednica (tool)\n\n### Autenticaci\u00f3n\n- Django: Header Auth credential (Api-Key)\n- WhatsApp: Header Auth credential (Bearer token Meta)\n- URLs via $env.DJANGO_API_URL\n\n### Estructura petici\u00f3n POST para probar webhook:\nhttps://n8n.alt4ir.online/webhook-test/whatsapp-inbound\n\nHeaders: Authorization Token {Auth Token}\n\n{\n    \"object\": \"whatsapp_business_account\",\n    \"entry\": [{\n      \"changes\": [{\n        \"value\": {\n          \"messages\": [{\n            \"from\": \"34644520621\",\n            \"id\": \"test-msg-001\",\n            \"timestamp\": \"1234567890\",\n            \"text\": { \"body\": \"Hola, quiero pedir cita\" },\n            \"type\": \"text\"\n          }],\n          \"contacts\": [{\n            \"profile\": { \"name\": \"Usuario Test\" },\n            \"wa_id\": \"34644520621\"\n          }],\n          \"metadata\": {\n            \"phone_number_id\": \"test-phone-id\"\n          }\n        }\n      }]\n    }]\n  }",
        "height": 680,
        "width": 580
      },
